title: Amy's Drive Thru
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Pizza, Western, Fast food, Take-out
description: Open July 2015 a vegetarian drive-through going head-to-head with a typical fast food places. Using Amy's Kitchen's own line of products, the menu offers veggie burgers, burritos, macaroni and cheese, pizza, salad, chili, as well as milkshakes and vegan non-dairy shakes. Each menu item can be ordered vegan or gluten-free.
